text: Death in Sarajevo () is a 2016 Bosnian drama movie directed by Danis Tanović and starring Snezana Markovic, Izudin Bajrovic, Vedrana Seksan, Muhamed Hadzovic, Faketa Salihbegovic, Edin Avdagic Koja, Jacques Weber. == Other websites == * Category:2016 drama movies Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina movies Category:Movies directed by Danis Tanović
title: Death in Sarajevo
